            Did he do wrong? The
<NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</NUMEX> question to ask is what the right thing would have been. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Kazan</ENAMEX> might have
stood by his original policy, asserting that while he hated Communism, he would
not assist in a violation of civil liberties. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Kazan</ENAMEX>'s soon to be ex-friend
