implied agreeing that simply being a <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Communist</ENAMEX> was a crime. Also, there is no
<ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">Fifth Amendment</ENAMEX> right against incriminating others. Unfortunately, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Supreme</ENAMEX>
