<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">villain</ENAMEX> doesn't make him a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">hero</ENAMEX>, either. Where <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Kazan</ENAMEX> did go wrong was in
